# Jvkrog — Autonomous Systems & Decision Engineering

> Building autonomous systems that observe, decide, and act with minimal human dependency.

---

## Featured Projects

### TAlgo-X — Multi-Engine Trading Infrastructure

Production-grade autonomous trading infrastructure built around adaptive execution logic, regime-aware filtering, and deterministic runtime behavior.

* Dual-engine architecture (FAST + SLOW ALMA execution layers)
* ADX and RSI-based trend-strength and volatility filtering
* Adaptive regime-aware signal generation
* Position persistence using SQLite
* Session lifecycle management and EOD risk controls
* Real-time Telegram monitoring and alert pipeline
* Structured runtime logging and explainable execution flow

---

### TAlgo — Adaptive Trading Engine

Real-time rule-based trading engine focused on systematic execution and emotional-risk reduction.

* Event-driven architecture (WebSocket + OHLC pipeline)
* EMA, HMA, and ALMA-based signal systems
* Runtime state-machine decision architecture
* Explainable signal generation and execution logs
* Risk-aware execution workflow with lifecycle controls

**Docs:**

* [Architecture](https://github.com/Jvkrog/TAlgo/blob/main/Docs/architecture.md)
* [Strategy](https://github.com/Jvkrog/TAlgo/blob/main/Docs/strategy.md)

---

### ALMA-Backtester-Python

Modular Python-based ALMA strategy backtesting framework with adaptive signal analysis, trade simulation, and visualization.

* ALMA slope-based BUY / SELL regime classification
* ATR-driven stop-loss and take-profit system
* Historical backtesting and equity curve analysis
* Trade lifecycle simulation and P&L tracking
* Multi-panel visualization dashboard
* Yahoo Finance market data integration

---

### WiFi Car (ESP32-CAM Rover)

Embedded robotic rover with real-time video streaming and browser-based navigation.

* ESP32-CAM live video streaming
* Wireless browser-controlled movement
* Embedded motor control using L298N
* Real-time remote navigation architecture

---

### FireBot

IoT-enabled mobile fire detection and monitoring system.

* Sensor-driven fire detection
* Real-time alert pipeline
* Remote monitoring capability
* Embedded safety-focused architecture

---

### Smart Wrist Band

Wearable safety and monitoring system with motion analysis and emergency alerts.

* MPU6050 motion sensing
* Fall-detection mechanism
* Blynk dashboard integration
* Telegram-based alert system

